@ClassVersion(sourceVersion="$Id: UMLMethodElement.java 976 2022-01-06 11:39:58Z tquadrat $") @API(status=INTERNAL, since="0.0.5") public final class UMLMethodElement extends UMLExecutableElement
The wrapper for an ExecutableElement instance that represents a constructor, enhanced by information needed for the creation of the UML graph.
